OL,3,C'Miracle' baby becomes youngest UK
OL,4,Cperson to have lifesaving blood
OL,5,Ctransfusion
OL,7,FArthur Ransom was at just 16 weeks
OL,8,Fgestation when he suffered heart
OL,9,Ffailure due to an infection, becoming
OL,10,Fthe youngest in the UK to have a life-
OL,11,Fsaving blood transfusion whilst still
OL,12,Fin the womb, as ITV News Correspondent
OL,13,FRachel Younger reports
OL,15,FA baby from Surrey is the youngest
OL,16,Fperson in the UK to have a lifesaving
OL,17,Fblood transfusion.
OL,19,FArthur Ransom was still in the womb
OL,20,Fwhen he suffered heart failure due to
OL,21,Fa viral infection.
