OL,3,C'Miracle' baby becomes youngest UK
OL,4,Cperson to have lifesaving blood
OL,5,Ctransfusion
OL,7,FHis mother Maisie, who was just 16
OL,8,Fweeks pregnant, was told it "would
OL,9,Ftake a miracle to save him."JHis
OL,10,Fchances of survival were so slim, they
OL,11,Fwere given the opportunity to
OL,12,Fterminate the pregnancy.
OL,14,FProfessor Asma Khalil suggested a
OL,15,Fprocedure so fraught with uncertainty.
OL,16,FEven she said it'd be a miracle if it
OL,17,Fworked.
