OL,3,C'Miracle' baby becomes youngest UK
OL,4,Cperson to have lifesaving blood
OL,5,Ctransfusion
OL,7,FHe needed a transfusion but at 16
OL,8,Fweeks was too small to have one via
OL,9,Fthe umbilical cord as is standard
OL,10,Fduring pregnancy.
OL,12,FInstead, he was put to sleep inside
OL,13,Fthe womb and a needle inserted into
OL,14,Fhis liver. It was a groundbreaking
OL,15,Fprocedure undertaken at London's St
OL,16,FGeorge's Hospital.
