OL,7,FA scan revealed that Arthur had
OL,8,Fparvovirus (also know as 'slapped
OL,9,Fcheek') which is largely harmless in
OL,10,Folder children. Maisie, a primary
OL,11,Fteacher, had unknowingly contracted it
OL,12,Fat school.
OL,14,FMum, Maisie told ITV News: "We were
OL,15,Ftold from the very first scans that he
OL,16,Fwas very poorly.
