OL,7,F"We could see ourselves from the scans
OL,8,Fthat his whole body was full of fluid,
OL,9,Fyou could see around his heart, there
OL,10,Fwas fluid everywhere. So we knew that
OL,11,Fhe was a really poorly baby.
OL,13,F"He's rolling and he's just starting
OL,14,Fto sit. We think he's perfect. We are
OL,15,Fso grateful."
OL,17,FProfessor Khalill said: "He's very
OL,18,Fhandsome. I can't stop looking at him.
OL,19,FHe's just so amazing, so healthy and
OL,20,Fdeveloping normally.
