OL,7,F"I would say there was a 50% chance of
OL,8,Flosing the baby. They are very tiny,
OL,9,Fthey are very small. You have to be
OL,10,Fvery precise because your target is
OL,11,Fliterally a couple of millimeters.
OL,13,F"So, if you miss your target but only
OL,14,Fa millimeter, you're not going to be
OL,15,Fable to achieve a successful
OL,16,Ftransfusion and it becomes a risky
OL,17,Fprocedure.
OL,19,F"Sometimes during this procedure or
OL,20,Fshortly afterwards you can lose the
OL,21,Fbaby."
